HEADWORD: Chuffy
<hw>Chuff"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Fat or
puffed out in the cheeks.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Rough; clownish; surly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

